                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="lead">
                        A comprehensive web application designed to streamline the process of booking and managing rooms 
                        for various purposes including meetings, conferences, workshops, and study sessions.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        Built with modern technologies and best practices, this system offers an intuitive interface 
                        combined with powerful features to eliminate scheduling conflicts and improve resource utilization.
                    </p>
