                                <i class="bi bi-bullseye text-primary"></i> Project Purpose
                            </h3>
                            <p>This system was developed to solve the common problem of double-booking and scheduling conflicts in shared spaces. It provides a centralized platform where users can:</p>
                            <ul class="mb-0">
                                <li>View available rooms with detailed information</li>
                                <li>Book rooms for specific time periods</li>
                                <li>Manage existing bookings efficiently</li>
                                <li>Avoid conflicts with automatic detection</li>
                            </ul>
